description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Low Pressure Cool-Down' from the channel Mac Evans.
The workout falls under Cool-down/Cool-down.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Comfort Moves vibe means Safe, cozy, feel-good movement. This is especially good for Those who want to move but need it to feel easy and accessible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Gradually bring down your heart rate with Mac by rowing at a walking pace. 

Max rhythm: 26, Format: Technique...
